      <title>西班牙试图推动欧盟关于夺取俄罗斯资产的辩论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/spain-seeks-to-push-forward-eu-debate-on-seizing-russian-assets</link>
