      <title>以色列告诉加沙人在“激烈战斗”之前离开南方</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/israel-tells-gazans-to-leave-border-area-before-intense-fight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列军队告诉巴勒斯坦人在加沙南部的地区离开哈马斯的“激烈战斗”，这是该标志，它计划扩展地面行动，以向激进组织施加压力，以释放仍被俘虏的人质。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/israel-tells-gazans-to-leave-border-area-before-intense-fight</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 10:29:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
